    Be part of the revolution in accessible blood testing. Get notified when Lifeline becomes available 
    and join our community of builders, researchers, and healthcare innovators.
  </p>
  
  <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mt-8 w-full max-w-md">
    <input 
      type="email" 
      placeholder="Enter your email" 
      class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border-0 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white focus:ring-opacity-50 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-white placeholder-gray-500 dark:placeholder-gray-400"
      required
    />
